  • public class AddressResult
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    Return object from AddressCandidate.getAddress() Different versions of ArcGis Server return different attributes for this object. If you can't access am attribute using one of the standard methods, then use getAddressValue where the key is the value you wish to access.
